Package de.htw.battleship

Class BattleshipApplication

java.lang.Object
de.htw.battleship.BattleshipApplication
public class BattleshipApplication
extends java.lang.Object
Requires Java 11 or higher. Contains the starting point for the application. An instance of this class can start new games, present the user different menus, call methods based on their choices and can save and load games and the High Score List.
